dct_title_s: Zimbabwe : Scale: 1:5,000  / this digital map was prepared jointly by Japan International Cooperation Agency (JICA) and the Department of the Surveyor-General of Zimbabwe under the Japanese Government Technical Cooperation Programme in the Republic of Zimbabwe.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "Compiled by stereo plotter from aerial photographs taken in July 2015, field check completion in 2016. "Copyright reserved by the Department of the Surveyor-General (DGS) Issued 12 sheets. There is not information whether is planned more sheet for this set. "The blue dashed straight lines in map represent location of existing map sheet referring Universal Transverse Mercator Grid on Modified Clarke 1880 Spheroid."
